16px; color: #1f2328; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , ' Noto Sans' , Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, ' Apple Color Emoji' , ' Segoe UI Emoji' font-size:14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li>画面の左上隅にある猫のアイコンをタップします</li><li>「スイッチ」アイコンをタップする：2本の青い猫の頭で正方形を探します</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0.25em; margin-left: 0px;\">「+」を選択します</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0.25em; margin-left: 0px;\">猫を選び、名前と年齢を入力してください</li></ul><p dir=\"auto\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1f2328; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , ' Noto Sans' , Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, ' Apple Color Emoji' , ' Segoe UI Emoji' font-size:14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: var(--base-text-weight-semibold, 600);\">スイッチングプロファイル</strong> </p><ul dir=\"auto\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 2em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1f2328; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , ' Noto Sans' , Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, ' Apple Color Emoji' , ' Segoe UI Emoji' font-size:14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-